00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:12.240
Welcome to the Nespresso Assistance video on cup size programming for your Lattissima Touch machine.

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.840
On this Nespresso machine you will find 6 beverage functions: 

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:22.920
Ristretto, Espresso, Lungo, Latte Macchiato, Cappuccino and warm milk froth. 

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:27.520
These preparations stop automatically when you have reached a specific volume. 

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.840
You can tailor the volume of these beverages to better suit your preferences.

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:40.000
Turn on your machine. It heats up for approximately 25 seconds.

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:50.720
Lift the lever completely and insert a capsule. Close the lever and place a cup under the coffee outlet.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:56.320
To begin, press and hold the desired coffee selection for 3 seconds.

00:00:56.680 --> 00:01:02.480
 This will enter programming mode, the button will blink fast and brewing will start.

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:07.400
Keep the button pressed for the entire process as the coffee flows.

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:12.000
Only release the button when the desired volume is reached.

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:16.880
It will blink three times to confirm the new volume has been stored. 

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:23.920
From this moment on, with one press on the button, the beverage will automatically flow to the programmed volume. 

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:32.560
Programming a Cappuccino

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:38.280
Open the steam connector door and put the Rapid Cappuccino System in place. 

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:40.960
It will take 15 seconds to heat. 

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:48.160
Then place a Cappuccino cup under the coffee outlet and adjust the milk spout by raising it to the right level.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:55.400
Adjust the texture of milk froth as required by turning the regulator knob left or right. 

00:01:55.840 --> 00:02:03.640
We recommend using Minimum milk froth texture for a Cappuccino and maximum milk froth texture for a Latte Macchiatto.

00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:08.720
To begin, press and hold the Cappuccino button for 3 seconds.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:15.560
This will enter programming mode, the button will blink fast and and warm milk froth will start

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:20.960
Keep the button pressed for the entire process as the warm milk froth flows. 

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:24.800
Only release the button when the desired volume is reached.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.920
Press and hold the same button for coffee brewing to start.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:32.520
Release the button when the desired coffee volume is reached.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.880
It will blink three times to confirm the new volume has been stored.

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:40.320
From this moment on, with one press on the cappuccino button,

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:45.280
the warm milk froth and coffee will automatically flow to the programmed volume. 

